<section sectnbr = "5C">
<servcat sctnbr = "05" scnbr = "03">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AHRAP70A5306018" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Uklanjanje i ugradnja poklopca i diska spojke
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A5306017">Komponente poklopca i diska spojke</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A5306018001">
<title>
Uklanjanje
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Demontirajte ručni mjenjač. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A5206010"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Držite zamašnjak specijalnim alatom i uklonite vijke poklopca spojke (1), poklopac spojke (2) i disk spojke.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5C001">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09924-17811">
09924-17811
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A531018.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.891mm" ver = "01" gw = "157" gh = "133"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AHRAP70A5306018002">
<title>
Ugradnja
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AHRAP70A5306019">Pregled poklopca i diska spojke</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Prije sastavljanja, uvjerite se da su površina zamašnjaka i površina potisne ploče čiste i temeljito osušene.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Držite zamašnjak specijalnim alatom (A).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5C002">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09924-17811">
09924-17811
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Poravnajte disk spojke sa sredinom koljenastog vratila korištenjem specijalnog alata (B) i ugradite poklopac spojke (1).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5C003">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09923-36320">
09923-36320
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ugradite i zategnite vijke poklopca spojke koristeći sljedeću proceduru:
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Rukom pritegnite 3 vijka (3) brojčanim redoslijedom (“1” do “3”).
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Postepeno i ravnomjerno zategnite preostala 3 vijka (4) momentom pritezanja od 5,0 N&#183;m (0,51 kgf-m, 4,0 lbf-ft) brojčanim redoslijedom (“4” do “6”).
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Postepeno i ravnomjerno zategnite do kraja sve vijke (3), (4) propisanim momentom pritezanja brojčanim redoslijedom (&#34;1&#34; do &#34;6&#34;), počevši od vijka pored zakovice ploče opružne noge (2).
</ptxt>
</s2>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Dok pritežete vijke poklopca spojke, uvjerite se da je utor diska spojke centriran tako da pritisnete specijalni alat na lamelu spojke.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T5C007">
<t-part>
Vijak poklopca spojke*
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-note>
5,0 N&#183;m &#8594; 23 N&#183;m (0,51 kgf-m &#8594; 2,3 kgf-m, 4,0 lbf-ft &#8594; 17,0 lbf-ft)
</t-note>
</torqueitem>
<torqueitem id = "T5C008">
<t-part>
Vijak poklopca spojke*
</t-part>
<t-part1>
b
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
23
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
2,3
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
17,0
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A531019.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "78.419mm" ver = "02" gw = "238" gh = "206"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Nanesite malo maziva na ulazno vratilo (1), zatim spojite ručni mjenjač na motor. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AHRAP70A5206010"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<materials>
<materialitem name = "SUZUKI Super Grease I" id = "M5C004" uid = "26">
<m-part>
“A”
</m-part>
<m-desc>
Mazivo
</m-desc>
<m-number>
99000-25210
</m-number>
<m-name>
SUZUKI Super Mast I
</m-name>
</materialitem>
</materials>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I6RS0E530018.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "45.655mm" ver = "01" gw = "135" gh = "113"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
